    "**Intimacy**: Tourism marriages often involve a smaller group of guests compared to traditional weddings.",
    "This can make the event more intimate and personal. 3.",
    "**Combination of Wedding and Honeymoon**: Many couples choose to have their honeymoon in the same location as their wedding, saving time and money. 4.",
    "**Unique Experiences**: Couples can incorporate local culture, traditions, or unique activities into their wedding, making it a memorable experience for everyone involved. 5.",
    "**Planning**: Planning a tourism marriage can be more complex than a local wedding."
